{"id":423172,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/12/423172/","date":"2015-12-29T23:03:37Z","modified":"2016-01-25T18:01:27Z","title":"文山娃：中國文人的“金蓮”情結——微博名士口業小錄","content":"<p>於中華傳統，有些個男性學者們繼承得最好的，恐怕就是“金蓮文化”——把對著女性比拼把玩色情文字的技巧，視為雅。</p>\n<p>【上流文人 下流表達 】</p>\n<p>老左識途：共青團網絡智庫專家 歐美同學會會員 微博社區專家委員<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/562D0BBC-AACC-45D6-A91F-17111FA4FD1D.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423181\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-423181\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/562D0BBC-AACC-45D6-A91F-17111FA4FD1D.jpg\" alt=\"562D0BBC-AACC-45D6-A91F-17111FA4FD1D\" width=\"440\" height=\"781\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/562D0BBC-AACC-45D6-A91F-17111FA4FD1D.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/562D0BBC-AACC-45D6-A91F-17111FA4FD1D-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p>戴旭：團中央網絡智庫專家 微博社區專家委員<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/92EB135F-E754-492F-9890-A1AB22A780DD.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423179\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-423179\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/92EB135F-E754-492F-9890-A1AB22A780DD.jpg\" alt=\"92EB135F-E754-492F-9890-A1AB22A780DD\" width=\"440\" height=\"781\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/92EB135F-E754-492F-9890-A1AB22A780DD.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/92EB135F-E754-492F-9890-A1AB22A780DD-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p>點子正：團中央網絡智庫專家 前新華社記者 瀋陽城市學院兼職教授<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/8F6AE7FA-AE1F-4AE5-8691-83402E2D6BAE.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423176\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-423176\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/8F6AE7FA-AE1F-4AE5-8691-83402E2D6BAE.jpg\" alt=\"8F6AE7FA-AE1F-4AE5-8691-83402E2D6BAE\" width=\"440\" height=\"781\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/8F6AE7FA-AE1F-4AE5-8691-83402E2D6BAE.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/8F6AE7FA-AE1F-4AE5-8691-83402E2D6BAE-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p>郭松民：前 空軍飛行員 《國企》雜誌研究部主任<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/ADDE9A76-F092-453A-95D0-F23573E452E6.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423184\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-423184\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/ADDE9A76-F092-453A-95D0-F23573E452E6.jpg\" alt=\"ADDE9A76-F092-453A-95D0-F23573E452E6\" width=\"440\" height=\"781\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/ADDE9A76-F092-453A-95D0-F23573E452E6.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/ADDE9A76-F092-453A-95D0-F23573E452E6-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p>椒江葉Sir：台州市公安局椒江分局民警 新浪微博社區專家委員 浙江最美警察候選人<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/466973AD-180D-438A-BC0D-F18626402F28.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423182\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-423182\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/466973AD-180D-438A-BC0D-F18626402F28.jpg\" alt=\"466973AD-180D-438A-BC0D-F18626402F28\" width=\"440\" height=\"781\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/466973AD-180D-438A-BC0D-F18626402F28.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/466973AD-180D-438A-BC0D-F18626402F28-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p>老辣陳香：台州市委宣傳部幹部<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/40F63163-813B-40FA-AF62-59F06045CB4D.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423178\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-423178\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/40F63163-813B-40FA-AF62-59F06045CB4D.jpg\" alt=\"40F63163-813B-40FA-AF62-59F06045CB4D\" width=\"440\" height=\"781\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/40F63163-813B-40FA-AF62-59F06045CB4D.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/40F63163-813B-40FA-AF62-59F06045CB4D-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p>孤煙暮蟬：惠州公務員<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/115D9E55-2D72-4621-B52F-8833A8B6EBE4.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423180\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-423180\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/115D9E55-2D72-4621-B52F-8833A8B6EBE4.jpg\" alt=\"115D9E55-2D72-4621-B52F-8833A8B6EBE4\" width=\"440\" height=\"781\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/115D9E55-2D72-4621-B52F-8833A8B6EBE4.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/115D9E55-2D72-4621-B52F-8833A8B6EBE4-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/0B35A052-5B15-43CB-BE51-9505A979A9DC.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423173\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-423173\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/0B35A052-5B15-43CB-BE51-9505A979A9DC.jpg\" alt=\"0B35A052-5B15-43CB-BE51-9505A979A9DC\" width=\"440\" height=\"1116\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/0B35A052-5B15-43CB-BE51-9505A979A9DC.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/0B35A052-5B15-43CB-BE51-9505A979A9DC-118x300.jpg 118w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/0B35A052-5B15-43CB-BE51-9505A979A9DC-404x1024.jpg 404w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p>郝連勃勃大王：國家一級作家 央視《百家講壇》主講<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/B1C449FC-74B6-42C4-97D1-0C2AC30B208E.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423185\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-423185\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/B1C449FC-74B6-42C4-97D1-0C2AC30B208E.jpg\" alt=\"B1C449FC-74B6-42C4-97D1-0C2AC30B208E\" width=\"440\" height=\"782\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/B1C449FC-74B6-42C4-97D1-0C2AC30B208E.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/B1C449FC-74B6-42C4-97D1-0C2AC30B208E-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p>胡楊麟：民間武裝運動導師<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/8BCFE88C-A7C1-48B6-AFC5-C453CA0F6BA5.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423175\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-423175\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/8BCFE88C-A7C1-48B6-AFC5-C453CA0F6BA5.jpg\" alt=\"8BCFE88C-A7C1-48B6-AFC5-C453CA0F6BA5\" width=\"440\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/8BCFE88C-A7C1-48B6-AFC5-C453CA0F6BA5.jpg 540w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/8BCFE88C-A7C1-48B6-AFC5-C453CA0F6BA5-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/1AB7DEF2-C0C8-49DD-B364-A37E43C01AEA.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423174\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-423174\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/1AB7DEF2-C0C8-49DD-B364-A37E43C01AEA.jpg\" alt=\"1AB7DEF2-C0C8-49DD-B364-A37E43C01AEA\" width=\"440\" height=\"781\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/1AB7DEF2-C0C8-49DD-B364-A37E43C01AEA.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/1AB7DEF2-C0C8-49DD-B364-A37E43C01AEA-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p>紀許光：前山東平度政府參事 美國華埠 『移民報』主編<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/A18F6539-76B7-495B-B9F8-0937F0963267.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423183\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-423183\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/A18F6539-76B7-495B-B9F8-0937F0963267.jpg\" alt=\"A18F6539-76B7-495B-B9F8-0937F0963267\" width=\"440\" height=\"781\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/A18F6539-76B7-495B-B9F8-0937F0963267.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/A18F6539-76B7-495B-B9F8-0937F0963267-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/A18F6539-76B7-495B-B9F8-0937F0963267-577x1024.jpg 577w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p>蔡小心：微博社區專家委員會成員 著名紅二代（註：核心）<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/31A4B08E-CA7E-4D33-B87F-E98CAA48DA4C.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-423177\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-423177\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/31A4B08E-CA7E-4D33-B87F-E98CAA48DA4C.jpg\" alt=\"31A4B08E-CA7E-4D33-B87F-E98CAA48DA4C\" width=\"440\" height=\"781\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/31A4B08E-CA7E-4D33-B87F-E98CAA48DA4C.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/31A4B08E-CA7E-4D33-B87F-E98CAA48DA4C-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p>上述公共知識份子，多有共青團智庫背景，亦多為新浪倚重并延請為微博社區專家委員。</p>\n<p>由此可見，團宣頗看中思想開放、語言犀利的人才。7月間，文登侯聚森等五人因打架被公安处理，一群古惑仔揮霍青春而已，結果變成今年比較重要的愛國示威遊行。最大的看点是舉國團宣的表現，紛紛表態力挺文登侯：一個有黃色語言天賦的紅色小孩。</p>\n<p>微博名士嘯聚，捫虱座談風月。</p>\n<p>坊間有詩贊這一時之盛：</p>\n<p>俱往矣！數下流人物，還看今朝。</p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,9203],"tags":[16016,20440,22684,29719,21038,21683,8636,26167,20688,26006]}